title: [1508521049] Best British Restaurant: The West House - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Gordon Ramsay in search of Britain's best restaurant. Top restaurants from around the UK compete to win the title. 

Ramsay visits, British restaurant, The west house, and passes judgement on the service.
